@@TJvFormPlace
Summary
  Component that remembers and restores a forms location.
Description
  Drop this component on a form if you want your application to remember the position and size of
  that form. This is especially useful for MDI forms, because users tend to arrange windows in a
  certain way.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvFormPlace.Remember
Summary
  Determines if the form location should be remembered/restored.
Description
  Remember determines if the form location should be remembered/restored.

  If set to True the size and position of the form are stored in the registry.

  If set to False the form behaves like a form without TJvFormPlace.
